create.prompt:
Use case: short playful social clip
Primary request: a monkey on roller skates
Scene/background: sunny beach boardwalk with pastel storefronts and palm trees, gentle sea breeze
Subject: a small stylized monkey wearing retro helmet and elbow pads
Action: glides forward, does a small spin, then waves at the camera
Camera: medium tracking shot, low angle, smooth dolly alongside
Lighting/mood: warm afternoon sunlight, cheerful
Color palette: teal, coral, sand, sunny yellow
Style/format: stylized 3D animation, clean render
Timing/beats: 0-2s glide, 2-3s spin, 3-4s wave
Constraints: no text, no logos
Avoid: flicker, jitter, heavy motion blur
